title: Jessica Biel Is Dressed Exactly Like A Golden Statue At 2017 Oscars
text:
Jessica Biel Is Dressed Exactly Like A Golden Statue At 2017 Oscars And it totally works. By Jamie Feldman 
Jessica Biel is a ray of golden sunshine on an otherwise gray day in Los Angeles on Sunday night. 
The 34-year-old arrived at the Oscars looking like an Oscar statue in a show-stopping gold gown complete with an an elaborate gold neckpiece. Kevin Mazur via Getty Images 
Biel, whose husband Justin Timberlake’s song “Can’t Stop the Feeling” is nominated for “Best Song,” looked stunning in the KaufmanFranco ensemble and a sleek updo. 
In a cheeky tweet, Biel thanked “everyone from the parts department to the folks on the assembly line for putting this package together.” I want to thank everyone from the parts department to the folks on the assembly line for putting this package together. #Oscars pic.twitter.com/9Ijlv1Q9ks — Jessica Biel (@JessicaBiel) February 27, 2017 
So. Stunning.
